tweet: You want to wake up in the morning and think that the future is going to be great - and that's what a spacefaring civilization is all about. It's about believing in the future will be better than the past. And I can't think of anything more exciting than goign out there and being among the stars.

Autopilot is an advanced driver assistance system that assists your car with steering, accelerating and braking other vehicles and pedestrians within its lane. It assists with the most burdensome parts of driving and work alongside features like emergency braking, collision warning and blind-spot monitoring. With Full Self-Driving (FSD) capability, you will get access to a suite of more advanced driver assistance features, designed to provide more active guidance and assisted driving under your active supervision.
